# Design Tokens

- Prefer token classes like `bg-primary`, `text-primary`, `border-primary`.
- Avoid hard-coded hex values in `className` when token exists.
- Keep app background white and typography scale consistent.
- Use spacing in 4px increments and consistent screen padding.
- Use established radius sizes for cards, inputs, buttons, and sheets.
